channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/bil7wh.png[/img]
Welcome To MindScape Pvp!
A revolutianary server
Much time spent coding
Attentive and dedicated staff
Looking for more coders who will receive a cut of all donations
Level Points
Voting System In Progress
Dupes Fixed
Join Now!
Webclient 1 - mindscapepvp.com/client
Webclient 2 - rswebclients.com/play/Mindscapee
Forums - mindscapepvp.com/forums/index.php
PK'ing [img]http://gyazo.com/39b799e816ae4184a026b50ba03270e4.png[/img] Frost Dragons [img]http://gyazo.com/5129213dc7bcf060807f2832b5493f27.png?1362685927[/img] Nomad [img]http://gyazo.com/76a2c59961266d5fcec6af347865ba5a.png[/img] Theres a lot to do on here, and we will be revamping the skilling area and home soon so be aware! :P
Notes: Server version: 317 Based of TrisidiaX [PI], we plan to edit it beyond limits, once we pickup a (few?) coder(s). Any questions feel free to ask.
[/center]
